      <title>法国总理有望度过不信任投票并通过预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/french-premier-set-to-survive-no-confidence-votes-adopt-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁将于周三安然度过两次不信任投票，这将为他实施推迟的 2025 年预算提供所需的稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/french-premier-set-to-survive-no-confidence-votes-adopt-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
