    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求裁员之际，中情局提供员工买断计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/cia-offers-staff-buyouts-as-trump-looks-to-shrink-workforce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中央情报局 (CIA) 已提出员工买断计划，以配合特朗普政府在政府范围内大范围裁员的举措，缩减员工数量，并加强该间谍机构对中国等首要任务的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/cia-offers-staff-buyouts-as-trump-looks-to-shrink-workforce</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
